♪ Hey, dog, hey, dog ♪

20:27.453 --> 20:29.453
♪ There's a little red rooster,
a little white hen ♪

20:29.455 --> 20:31.756
♪ Ain't had no lovin'
since I don't know when ♪

20:31.758 --> 20:34.792
♪ I wonder who's boogie'n
